This package and its subpackages provide backend features for the hu.elte.txtuml.api package to help in the model execution.

Package hu.elte.txtuml.api.backend Description

This package and its subpackages provide backend features for the hu.elte.txtuml.api package to help in the model execution. Is not part of the public API.
